        walkthrough = '1. Speak with Horatius inside of the Trader\'s Home at (I-9) in Bastok Markets, who sends you to Dangruf Wadi.\n   - The monsters in the area around the ??? are level 90-95. Only the Goblins are aggressive and they can be avoided with just Invisible since they do not have pets.\n     - You will lose Invisible when riding the geyser (I-8) at Dangruf Wadi, so Field Support from the Grounds Tome will fail. Refer to Invisible (Status) for other options.\n2. Inside Dangruf Wadi, head to the (I-5)/(J-5) boundary, where you\'ll find a ??? during sunny weather.\n   - Sunny weather is the default weather with no icon. If there is a weather at the time you\'re attempting this quest, you will have to wait for it to clear up to find the ???.\n   - You receive the Dangruf Stone after choosing the dialog option to check the area.\n3. Head back to Horatius for your reward of 400g.',
