        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Tami in Bastok Mines at (J-8) to begin quest.\n2. She will give you the [Key Item] Tami\'s note.\n   - Note: If you open and read the Key Item, you can no longer repeat the quest.\nIf you read the note\n3. Proceed to Zeruhn Mines and locate Zelman at (I-8).\n4. Go to (H-5) in Bastok Mines (Bat\'s Lair Inn) and purchase a Meat Jerky from Griselda.\n5. Trade the jerky to Tami for your reward of a Rabbit Mantle.\n   - You will now complete the quest, and it is no longer repeatable.\nIf you do not read the note\n6. Proceed to Zeruhn Mines and locate Zelman at (I-8).\n7. He will tell you that he is busy, and to tell Tami.\n8. Return to Tami for your reward of 10 Gil.\n   - At this point, you can repeat this quest.',
