        walkthrough = '1. If you have just completed Teak Me to the Stars, you must zone before starting this quest.\n2. Speak with Raibaht to begin quest. You will receive a [Key Item] Molybdenum box.\n3. Travel to Lower Delkfutt\'s Tower and proceed to the basement.\n   - A Delkfutt Key or [Key Item] Delkfutt key is required.\n4. Travel to (I-6) of the basement map and touch the Cermet Door to pop 3 NMs: Orna (the boss) and 2 Fomorian Spear.\n5. Defeat Orna (which will make the other two depop) and touch the Cermet Door again.\n6. Travel to Lower Jeuno and inspect the Street Lamp targets until you find a [Key Item] Hyper altimeter.\n7. Return to Bastok and speak with Raibaht to complete quest.',
