        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Hungry Wolf inside the Craftmen\'s Eatery to start the quest. (Use Home Point #1.)\n2. Obtain a Giant Sheep Meat from the Auction House or from Ornery Sheep in South Gustaberg (or elsewhere.)\n3. Travel to South Gustaberg (K-9) to find a Goblin campfire (???).\n   - To find this, look on your map for the small hill at (K-9). Proceed to the area directly south of the hill at the top of (K-10) and you\'ll see a ramp to go up the hill. It blends in with the surroundings, so keep an eye open for it.\n4. Trade the Giant Sheep Meat to the campfire and to begin to cook it.\n5. Wait for a minute (Earth time). DO NOT ZONE OUT, or you will have to repeat these steps again!\n6. After the required wait time, check the campfire again to receive a Galkan Sausage.\n   - It goes directly into your inventory, so make sure you have an open slot.\n7. Trade the Galkan Sausage to Hungry Wolf to complete the quest.',
