        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Malene to begin quest.\n2. Obtain a Steam Clock via the following methods:\n      - Purchase via Auction House\n      - Defeat Bubbly Bernie. To spawn Bubbly Bernie, acquire a Quus (fish) either via Auction House or by fishing. Travel to the light house in South Gustaberg (M-10) and look for a ???. Trade the Quus to the ??? and Bubbly Bernie will pop in to say hi. Proceed to maul him, once defeated you may loot his corpse for a Steam Clock.\n3. Return to town and trade the clock to Malene to complete quest.',
