        start_zone = 'Bastok Mines',
        start_pos = 'J-9',
        description = 'Phara needs some sword grip material\nto repair her son\'s sword.\nThe material can be found in a tent\nin Davoi.\nOnce repaired, Phara wants to give\nthe sword to her grandson.',
        reward = 'Razor Axe',
        fame = 'Bastok',
        fame_level = '1',
        title = 'None',
        repeatable = 'No',
        previous = nil,
        next = {'The Talekeeper\'s Truth'},
        requirements = {
            {name = '[Key Item] Sword grip material', count = 1},
        },
        walkthrough = '1. Talk to Phara in Bastok Mines at (J-9).\n   - She is right beside the Gobbie Mystery Box at HP #2.\n2. Go to Davoi and click the Hide Flap at K-9/10.\n   - This Pops 2 NM\'s Barakbok and Gavotvut.\n3. Kill them then check the Hide Flap to receive the [Key Item] Sword grip material.\n   - The Hide Flap moves to a random spot in this area once you check it. It can be in the same spot.\n   - If multiple people are doing the quest, you will have to wait 5 min to pop again.\n4. Speak to Phara then wait a game day (after clock rolls around past 00:00).\n5. Speak to Phara again for [Key Item] Yasin\'s sword.\n6. Speak to Naji outside the President\'s Office in Metalworks at (J-8) for a cutscene to finish the quest and receive your Razor Axe.  You may have to speak to him twice.',
