        walkthrough = '1. After just completing Hearts of Mythril, you must zone in order to flag this quest.\n2. Speak to Elki to start quest.\n3. Travel to  the top floor of Palborough Mines (Map 3).\n   - Palborough Mines Home Point #1 is the fastest.\n4. Examine the Old Toolbox at the intersection of (H-7)/(H-8) to receive the Key Item Old toolbox.\n5. Return to Elki and speak to him.\n6. After the cutscene, speak to Babenn in Bastok Mines (J-6) to complete quest.',
