        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Michea to start quest\n2. Obtain a Copper Ingot from either the Auction House, Goldsmithing guild shops or by crafting it.\n      - (Recommended method) To buy the Copper Ore to craft the Ingot from a guild shop, visit the following NPCs:\n         - Teerth  Bastok Markets (H-8)\n         - Visala  Bastok Markets (H-8)\n         - Yabby Tanmikey  Mhaura (G-8)\n         - Celestina  Mhaura (G-8)\n      - To craft the ingot:\n         - Use a Fire Crystal with 4 Copper Ores\n3. Trade the Ingot to Michea to complete the quest.\n4. May be repeated by zoning out of the area. No longer repeatable once you attain Bastok fame level 2.',
