        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Clarion Star in Port Bastok HP #1 at (K-7), he will give you the [Key Item] Blue institute card.\n2. Head to Metalworks HP #1 (J-8) and speak to Naji.\n   - If this is not your first Trust quest that you are completing, at this point you will be finished with the Quest and receive the [Key Item] Bastok Trust permit.\n   - If this is your first Trust Quest, you must use the Trust magic spell "Naji" in either South Gustaberg or North Gustaberg. After, return to Naji for the [Key Item] Bastok Trust permit.',
