        walkthrough = '1. Speak to Zacc (G-9) who is standing next to Enu (G-9).\n2. Speak with Malene (I-5), more popularly known as the Steam Clock/Bubbly Bernie quest giver.\n3. Return to the fountain and speak with Enu.\n   - The quest will now appear in your log.\n4. Acquire a Hatchet from the Auction House, NPC stores, or crafting.\n5. Travel to Yuhtunga Jungle and locate a Logging Point. Start logging and you will receive a Fallen Star.\n   - Yuhtunga Jungle is on Elshimo Island, accessed via airship with [Key Item] Kazham Airship Pass or transport to Norg via NPCs in Mhaura or Selbina (requires RoV 1-5 or later).\n6. Return to Enu and trade her the star on a clear starry night (Clear weather, with stars visible in the sky) to complete the quest.\n   - Attempts during other weather conditions, including Clear weather but with overcast (clouds), will cause Enu to say "It has to be a starry night for the fallen star to work. We have to wait a little bit longer."',
